title: Episode 56 w/ French Montana, T.I. and A$AP Rocky

description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up in Los Angeles with French Montana, T.I. and A$AP Rocky. They cover everything from Donald Trump, Kanye for president, to how to maintain longevity in the industry and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
